InputField - Class in no.hist.aitel.team12.gui
An extension of JTextField to support a default text that goes away when the field gets focus.
InputField(String, int) - Constructor for class no.hist.aitel.team12.gui.InputField
Sole constructor.
It is equal to JTextField(int columns), but with the additional default text property.
Simply set this to an empty string to make it behave like the standard JTextField
